Thales’s French Customers Satisfaction Drops, La Tribune Reports

-- B y   H e l e n e   F o u q u e t
-- 
2011-06-27T17:53:39Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-27/thales-s-french-customers-satisfaction-drops-la-tribune-reports.html
Thales SA (HO) ’s French customers
satisfaction fell 13 percent on average between 2008 and 2010,
an internal survey obtained by  La Tribune  showed.  The survey was conducted in the fall of last year and
included customers in  France ’s armed forces and in aeronautics
and defense industries, the newspaper reported. A call to the
company’s offices was unanswered outside of office hours.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
James Hertling at   jhertling@bloomberg.net  